  "supported_languages": "English, French, German, Spanish - Spain, Japanese, Korean, Portuguese - Brazil, Russian, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese",
  "reviews": "\u201cKatana Zero's adrenaline pumping action is incredible and its presentation is stellar...\u201d<br>8.7/10 \u2013 <a href=\"https://www.ign.com/articles/2019/04/18/katana-zero-review\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >IGN</a><br><br>\u201cKatana Zero is bloody and brutal, but it's also a heartfelt tale that you shouldn't overlook lightly.\u201d<br>8/10 \u2013 <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/katana-zero-review-slow-motion-samurai/1900-6417126/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Gamespot</a><br><br>\u201cFew games match the execution and style like Katana Zero.\u201d<br>9/10 \u2013 <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.usgamer.net/articles/katana-zero-review\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >USGamer</a><br>",
